<br>
This is a summary of the Necromancer epic quest for the Scythe of the Shadowed Soul.<br>
<br>
Quest Start<br>
<br>
Talk to the Female Dark elf by the river in Nektulos Forest to start the quest.<br>
<br>
<br>
Go to Lake Rathetear. Talk to Kazen Facae. <br>
Go to East Freeport. Find and kill Sir Edwin Motte to get his head. <br>
Go to Lake Rathe. Give Motte's head to Kazen Facae to get the Symbol of the Apprentice. <br>
Go to Nektulos Forest. Give the Symbol of the Apprentice to the dark elf that gave you the quest to get the Twisted Symbol of the Apprentice. <br>
Go to Najena. Kill Najena to get the Flowing Black Robe. <br>
Go to Nektulos Forest. Give the Flowning Black Robe to the dark elf that gave you the quest to get the moss. <br>
Go to Lake Rathetear. Give the moss and Twisted Symbol of the Apprentice to Emkel to get the Symbol of the Serpent. <br>
Go to Swamp of No Hope. Give the Symbol of the Serpent to Ssessthrass to get the Scaled Symbol of the Serpent. <br>
Go to Chardok. Kill the Royal Herbalist to get the Manisi Herb. <br>
Go to Swamp of No Hope. Give the Scaled Symbol of the Serpent and the Manisi Herb to Ssessthrass to get the Refined Manisi Herb. <br>
Go to Lake Rathetear. Give the Refined Manisi Herb to Emkel to get the Symbol of Testing. <br>
Give the Symbol of Testing to Kazen Facae and three mobs will spawn. <br>
Kill all three mobs to get the Symbol of Insanity. <br>
Go to Timorous Deep. Give the Symbol of Insanity to Drendico Metalbones to get his journal. <br>
Go to Plane of Sky. Do the Cloak of Spiroc Feathers quest to get the Cloak of Spiroc Feathers.<br>
[NOTE: See below for the quest.] <br>
Go to Plane of Hate. Kill Innoruuk to get the Eye of Innoruuk. <br>
Go to Plane of Fear. Kill Cazic Thule to get the Blood of Cazic Thule. <br>
Go to Timorous Deep. Give the Cloak of Spiroc Feathers, Eye of Innoruuk, Blood of Cazic Thule and Drendico's Journal to Drendico Metalbones to get the Prepared Reagent Box. <br>
Go to Lake Rathetear. Give the Prepared Reagent Box to Kazen Facae to get the Tome of Instruction. <br>
Go to Plane of Sky. Go to Island 3 and give Gkzzallk the Tome of Instruction to get Gkzzallk in Box. <br>
Go to Lake Rathetear. Give Gkzzallk in Box to Kazen Facae to get the Scythe of the Shadowed Soul. <br>
<br>
<br>
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
<br>
Sub-Quest: Cloak of Spiroc Feathers<br>
<br>
<br>
Hail and talk to Drakis Bloodcaster in the Plane of Sky to start the quest. <br>
Then talk to Jzil GSix. <br>
Go to Island 3. Kill the Azeraks to get the Silver Disk. <br>
Go to Island 4. Kill mobs to get the Spiroc Feather. <br>
Go to Island 5. Kill the Keeper of Souls to get the Black Silk Cape. <br>
Turn in all three items to get the Cloak of Spiroc Feathers. <br>
